Package com.root14.barcodeservice.core

Enum Class BarcodeType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<BarcodeType>
com.root14.barcodeservice.core.BarcodeType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<BarcodeType>, Constable
public enum BarcodeType extends Enum<BarcodeType>
An enumeration representing different types of barcodes supported by the service. Each enum constant maps to a specific Writer class from the Google ZXing library and its corresponding BarcodeFormat. This enum facilitates easy lookup and association of barcode types with their respective writer implementations and formats.
